description: Passengers flying via Swedish airports fell 4% in 2019, airport operators Swedavia say.
title: Sweden sees rare fall in air passengers, as flight-shaming takes off
title_page: Sweden sees rare fall in air passengers, as flight-shaming takes off - BBC News
maintext: Aside from Sweden, Europe is still seeing an increase in the number of people flying. The EU overall saw figures rise to 1.1 billion passengers in 2018, up from 1 billion the year before.
